# Bayesian FM Contextual Bandit Thesis (Simulation)

This repo runs simulation experiments for contextual bandits:
- Random baseline
- Logistic Thompson Sampling baseline
- Bayesian FM + Thompson Sampling (proposed)

## Setup

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install -e .
